{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8bd32f469a","title":"关于越南人民军的作战规模的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dddc0744a3","index":0,"year":1954,"month":6,"day":20,"articleId":"8bd32f469a"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"c5fd2660cb","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"日内瓦国际会议于1954年7月21日就印度支那停战和恢复和平问题达成了协议。"},{"id":"5cdf2aa1d8","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"韦国清，当时任驻越南军事顾问团团长。"},{"id":"a2da7561c4","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡，指胡志明，当时任越南民主共和国政府主席。武，指武元甲，当时任越南民主共和国国防部部长兼越南人民军总司令。韦，指韦国清。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6d7f6a35c8","type":"title","text":"关于越南人民军的作战规模的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a"},{"id":"c5fd2660cb","type":"paragraph","text":"广西省委转周恩来同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a"},{"id":"5cdf2aa1d8","type":"paragraph","text":"在日内瓦会议有进展并可能在七月达成停战协议\"的情况下，越南人民军的作战规模以不要扩大也不要缩小即保持现在的规模似较适宜。前些日子韦国清同志电告越军作了一个新部署，准备在七月内把战争规模略为扩大。我们认为可以照韦电增加一部分军队于红河三角洲区域，以威肠法国人，但七月不要大打。何时可以大打，应完全依日内瓦会议情况作决定。以上意见是否妥当，请与胡、武、韦三同志的定","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a"},{"id":"a2da7561c4","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a"},{"id":"60464cb57f","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a"}],"page":{"id":"2b67b6695c","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"8bd32f469a","start":144,"end":144}}}},"__N_SSG":true}